name: TerraReal
description:
**THERE IS A BUG WHERE YOU CANT MOVE, THIS IS NOT OUR TAKE ON THE THEME. TRY RELOADING**

Made in 7 days for the Brackeys jam with the theme It is not real. This game fits the theme because you can make the ground not real.

Controls
  • Move: Arrows/WASD
  • Jump: X/W/Up Arrow/Space
  • Change Ground: Z
  • Interact: C
  • Restart: R
Credit
